'''墓蝠屬'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Taphozous''}}），[[哺乳綱|哺乳綱]]、[[翼手目|翼手目]]、[[鞘尾蝠科|鞘尾蝠科]]的一屬[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]。

==下属物种==
* [[南墓蝠|南墓蝠]] (昆士蘭墓蝠) - ''Taphozous australis'' (Coastal tomb bat)
* [[尖吻墓蝠|尖吻墓蝠]] (尖鼻墓蝠) - ''Taphozous georgianus'' (Sharp-nosed tomb bat)
* [[苏丹墓蝠|苏丹墓蝠]] (哈氏墓蝠) - ''Taphozous hamiltoni'' (Hamilton's tomb bat)
* [[肯尼亚墓蝠|肯尼亚墓蝠]] (希氏墓蝠) - ''Taphozous hildegardeae'' (Hildegarde's tomb bat)
* [[希氏墓蝠|希氏墓蝠]] - ''Taphozous hilli'' (Hill's tomb bat)
* [[澳洲墓蝠|澳洲墓蝠]] (白紋墓蝠) - ''Taphozous kapalgensis'' (Arnhem tomb bat)
* [[長臂墓蝠|長臂墓蝠]] - ''Taphozous longimanus'' (Long-winged tomb bat)
* [[南非墓蝠|南非墓蝠]] - ''Taphozous mauritianus'' (Mauritian tomb bat)
* [[黑髯墓蝠|黑髯墓蝠]] (黑鬚墓蝠) - ''Taphozous melanopogon'' (Black-bearded tomb bat)
* [[裸腹墓蝠|裸腹墓蝠]] - ''Taphozous nudiventris'' (Naked-rumped tomb bat)
* [[埃及墓蝠|埃及墓蝠]] - ''Taphozous perforatus'' (Egyptian tomb bat)
* [[菲律賓墓蝠|菲律賓墓蝠]] - ''Taphozous philippinensis'' (Philippine tomb bat)
* [[西氏墓蝠|西氏墓蝠]] (席氏墓蝠) - ''Taphozous theobaldi'' (Theobald's tomb bat)

